## 📋 Description
This PR adds a complete Random Joke Generator feature to the ACMEuniverse mobile app. Users can generate random jokes, filter by type, and save their favorites.

## ✨ Features Added
- **Joke Generator Screen**: Display random jokes with setup and punchline
- **Joke Type Filter**: Filter jokes by type (random, general, knock-knock, programming)
- **External API Integration**: Using Official Joke API (https://official-joke-api.appspot.com)
- **Favorites System**: Save and manage favorite jokes
- **Favorites Screen**: View all saved favorite jokes
- **Home Screen**: Navigation hub for app features
- **Error Handling**: Proper error messages and loading states
- **Modern UI**: Material Design with responsive layouts

## 🔧 What Changed
- Added `lib/models/joke_model.dart` - Joke data model
- Added `lib/services/joke_service.dart` - API service for fetching jokes
- Added `lib/screens/joke_generator_screen.dart` - Main joke generator UI
- Added `lib/screens/home_screen.dart` - Home screen with navigation

## 🎯 How It Works
1. User selects joke type from dropdown
2. App fetches joke from external API
3. Display setup and punchline
4. User can favorite jokes
5. View all favorites in separate screen

